      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows significant signs of use. There are noticeable cosmetic imperfections on the exterior, including scratches and minor dents, and the interior shows wear. All major systems are operational, but some minor electronic features may be intermittent.",
